  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the wife of Ser Benfrey Frey, see <a href=\"/index.php/Jyanna_Frey\" title=\"Jyanna Frey\">Jyanna Frey</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><img alt=\"No image.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/50px-No_image.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/75px-No_image.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/100px-No_image.svg.png 2x\" /></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Jyana</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Reed\" title=\"House Reed\"><img alt=\"House Reed.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/House_Reed.svg/50px-House_Reed.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/House_Reed.svg/75px-House_Reed.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b6/House_Reed.svg/100px-House_Reed.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of <a href=\"/index.php/Greywater_Watch\" title=\"Greywater Watch\">Greywater Watch</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Reed\" title=\"House Reed\">House Reed</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crannogmen\" title=\"Crannogmen\">Crannogmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">Howland Reed</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera Reed</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jyana</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Crannogmen\" title=\"Crannogmen\">crannogwoman</a> and the wife of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">Howland Reed</a>. Together they have two children: <a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jyana&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"